---
import Layout from '@layouts/Default.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure - Highest Liked"
  pageTitle="HighestLiked - Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="Learn about HighestLiked's affiliate relationships and how we curate products."
>
  <main class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-16 md:py-24">
      <h1 class="libre-baskerville-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-black mb-8 leading-tight">
        Affiliate Disclosure
      </h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p class="text-lg">
            HighestLiked participates in the <strong>Amazon Services LLC Associates Program</strong> — an affiliate advertising program that allows websites to earn small commissions by linking to products on Amazon.com.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg">
            Since its creation, HighestLiked has focused on curating the internet's most loved, most viral, and most wishlist-worthy products — the kind people can't stop sharing.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg">
            <strong>We never feature items just to earn a commission.</strong> Every product shown is something that genuinely caught our attention for its creativity, usefulness, or wow factor. If an affiliate link exists, we'll use it — but it never decides what gets featured.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-lg">
            Clicking a link or making a purchase through HighestLiked never changes the price you pay. It simply helps support the site so we can keep uncovering the internet's favorites.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-200">
          <a 
            href="/" 
            class="inline-flex items-center text-[#6366f1] hover:text-[#8b5cf6] font-semibold transition-colors"
          >
            <svg 
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
              class="h-5 w-5 mr-2" 
              fill="none" 
              viewBox="0 0 24 24" 
              stroke="currentColor"
            >
              <path 
                stroke-linecap="round" 
                stroke-linejoin="round" 
                stroke-width="2" 
                d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" 
              />
            </svg>
            Back to Home
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .libre-baskerville-bold {
    font-family: "Libre Baskerville", serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .prose {
    color: #374151;
  }

  .prose strong {
    color: #111827;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
</style>

